    <stitle>FRONT NON-DRIVE STEERING AXLE: ROCKWELL - CLEAN AND INSPECT - CLEANING THE ROUGH PARTS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="repair" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEANING THE ROUGH PARTS</title>
        <para>Rough parts can be cleaned with the ground or polished parts. Rough parts also can be cleaned in hot
            solution tanks with a weak alkaline solution. Parts must remain in the hot solution tanks until they are
            completely cleaned and heated.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
